This is the intro, taking you up to the chorus. ("Good Times,  
Bad Times...")  There are actually two guitars here, but I`ve  
tried to simplify things as much as possible for one.  Also,  
watch for minor changes in the fingering, as there are changes  
not only between the hammers-on and slides of the two guitar  
parts, but between each time the bit is repeated.  My symbols  
above the TAB, "[:  :]x mean to repeat everything betweeen the  
brackets and colons, and do it the number of times followed by  
"x", in this case five times.  
     -Dave  
  
